    "title": "Mid-Level Plant Manager at Adani Enterprises Advisory Limited",
    "description": "Grow your career with Adani Enterprises Advisory Limited! We are hiring a Plant Manager for our Dhanbad team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout Adani Enterprises Advisory Limited:\nAdani Enterprises Advisory Limited is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Coordinate with logistics for dispatching finished goods\n• Manage supplier quality audits and vendor development\n• Coordinate with design and engineering teams on product improvements\n• Monitor equipment performance and coordinate preventive maintenance\n• Conduct root cause analysis for quality rejections and defects\n• Implement lean manufacturing and continuous improvement initiatives\n• Ensure compliance with safety regulations and factory acts\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Bachelor's degree in a relevant field\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in SolidWorks\n• Proficiency in AutoCAD\n• Proficiency in 5S\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain Management\n• Proficiency in GD&T\n• Proficiency in Statistical Process Control\n• Proficiency in TPM\n• Proficiency in PPAP\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Learning & development budget\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Dhanbad, Jharkhand, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Adani Enterprises Advisory Limited!",
